ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to provide the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness (or a delegate of the Minister) with the authority to issue a departure order to a foreign national on a final determination that his or her refugee protection status has ceased as a result of cessation proceedings at the the Refugee Protection Division.
